└── README.md
```

---

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/Python-Mini-Projects.git
```

2. Open the project folder

```bash
cd Python-Mini-Projects
```

3. Run any project

```bash
python todo_list.py
```

or

```bash
python expense_tracker.py
```

or

```bash
python password_generator.py
```

---

